---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import ProcessSteps from '../components/ProcessSteps.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Odor Removal Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional car odor removal in Fort Lauderdale. Mobile service - we come to you! Eliminates smells at the source, not just covers them. Same-day appointments. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}upholstery-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Upholstery Cleaning Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Odor Removal Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional odor removal eliminates bad smells from your car by treating the source, not just covering it up with air fresheners."
  currentPage="/odor-removal-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Air fresheners and sprays only mask odors temporarily. The smell always comes back because the source is still there. True odor removal means finding what's causing the smell, treating it directly, and eliminating it permanently.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We bring our odor removal service directly to your home or office anywhere in Fort Lauderdale. From homes near Las Olas Boulevard to apartments in Victoria Park, we come to you with professional equipment and products that actually work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Florida's humidity makes car odors worse than anywhere else. Moisture feeds the bacteria and mold that create bad smells. What might be a minor odor up north becomes a serious problem in our climate.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Much Does Car Odor Removal Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Car odor removal in Fort Lauderdale costs $75 to $200 depending on the odor source and treatment needed.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Light odors from food or mildew fall on the lower end. Severe odors from pet accidents, spoiled food, or mold require more intensive treatment. Ozone treatment for stubborn smells costs more but delivers results when other methods fail.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We'll diagnose your situation and give you options before starting any work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Long Does Odor Removal Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Odor removal takes 1 to 2 hours depending on the treatment method and severity of the smell.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Basic odor treatment involves cleaning the source and applying odor eliminators. More stubborn smells may need ozone treatment, which requires the car to sit closed for an hour while the ozone machine runs. Severe cases might need the process repeated.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Your car is ready to drive after treatment, though ozone-treated vehicles need to air out for 15-20 minutes first.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Why Do Cars Develop Bad Odors in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Florida's heat and humidity accelerate odor development. Food spoils faster, moisture breeds mold, and bacteria thrive in warm, damp conditions.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Common odor sources in Fort Lauderdale vehicles:</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Mildew</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Moisture from rain, wet swimsuits, or humidity gets trapped and grows mold. That musty smell is mildew spores.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Food</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Forgotten items spoil quickly in Florida heat. Even crumbs can attract moisture and start smelling.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Spills</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Drinks that soak into carpet or seats feed bacteria as they break down.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Pet Accidents</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Urine soaks deep into carpet padding and requires enzymatic treatment to fully eliminate.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">AC System</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Mold grows in your air conditioning evaporator, blowing musty air every time you run the AC.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Body Odor</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sweat absorbed by seats over time creates a sour smell.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Signs you need professional odor removal:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Bad smell returns after cleaning or air fresheners</li>
          <li>You can't identify where the smell is coming from</li>
          <li>The odor gets worse on hot days</li>
          <li>Your AC blows musty-smelling air</li>
          <li>Passengers comment on the smell</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-6">Our Odor Removal Process</h2>
        <ProcessSteps steps={[
          { title: "Source Identification", description: "We find where the smell is coming from. This determines the right treatment approach." },
          { title: "Deep Cleaning", description: "We clean the affected area thoroughly. You can't eliminate odors without removing what's causing them." },
          { title: "Enzymatic Treatment", description: "For organic odors like food, pet accidents, or body fluids, we apply enzyme-based products that break down odor-causing molecules." },
          { title: "Ozone Treatment", description: "For stubborn odors, we run an ozone generator inside your sealed car. Ozone molecules attach to odor particles and neutralize them permanently." },
          { title: "AC Treatment", description: "If the smell comes from your air system, we treat the evaporator and vents to kill mold and bacteria." },
          { title: "Final Check", description: "We verify the odor is gone before finishing." }
        ]} />
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-2">Pet Accident Note</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          For pet accidents, enzymatic treatment is essential. Regular cleaning only masks the smell temporarily. The urine proteins break down and smell worse over time unless treated with enzymes that destroy them completely.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Odor Removal Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c0c7cf] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$75-$200 depending on severity</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">1-2 hours</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Ozone treatment available</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Treats source, not symptoms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Permanent results</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#0f2a4a] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Odor Removal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}smoke-odor-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Smoke Odor Removal</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}pet-hair-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Pet Hair Removal</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}steam-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Steam Cleaning</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}seat-shampooing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Seat Shampooing</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
